DEPENDENCY NOTICE
-----------------

This plugin depends on third-party libraries with the following licenses:

  - QGIS (GPL-2.0-or-later)         https://qgis.org
  - PyQt5 (GPL-3.0)                  https://riverbankcomputing.com/software/pyqt
  - GDAL/OGR (MIT/X)                 https://gdal.org
  - libheif (LGPL-3.0-or-later)      https://github.com/strukturag/libheif
  - Pillow (HPND)                    https://python-pillow.org
  - pillow-heif (BSD-3-Clause)       https://github.com/bigcat88/pillow_heif
  - rdflib (BSD-3-Clause)            https://rdflib.readthedocs.io

All dependencies are compatible with GPL-3.0-or-later.
The use of PyQt5 (GPL-3.0) makes this the minimum license for distribution.
